{"tid":1855920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郵政工會稱空郵中心積存逾萬特快郵件　當中八成為口罩","createTime":"2020-02-01T10:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T15:44:22.000Z","uid":29675,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f9df8a094cf38679c4e738590b8d1626099fa5f1","tid":1855920,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:33:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506059-20200201.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506059-20200201.htm&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ij4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=ba0fe1ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506059-20200201.htm&h=d5fd0efd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506059-20200201.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n因應疫情，不少市民近日從外地網購平台購買口罩。據郵政局員工會的了解，空郵中心積存的萬件特快專遞郵件中，有8成為口罩，空郵中心職員已彈性處理，優先處理寄往住宅的口罩郵件。<br />\n<br />\n郵政局員工會主席葉錦富表示，據他了解，農曆年假期以來，機場空郵中心已積存一萬件特快專遞郵件，以及8000件普通包裹。當中特快專遞郵件中，按貨品報關資料，估計有8成為口罩，空郵中心職員自行彈性處理，優先取出以住宅為地址的口罩郵件送往派遞中心。<br />\n<br />\n葉錦富說，口罩郵件來源以日本和南韓最多，亦有來自台灣、泰國、澳洲、美加等地。空郵中心每天亦會接收約3000件特快專遞郵件及1500件普通包裹，但因應部門目前實施特別上班安排，上班人數只佔約一半，吞吐量與平日有差别。<br />\n<br />\n葉錦富說，部門目前只提供口罩及酒精搓水液，並無提供手套及其他防護裝備，郵務員按工作需要到醫院等地方，亦要處理包括來自內地的郵件，希望管理層短期內加強員工的防護裝備，部門已承諾若未能及時提供手套，員工可先行購買其後再申索有關金額。<br />\n<br />\n郵差叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2028d6392973d45f043f5cdb5269e340311759","tid":1855920,"uid":271747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"多謝郵差叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc23c5d637f96ffc667bcb0903ff5f1e5632efd","tid":1855920,"uid":11071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f04fe564fcb8be25a0533574292dfda7dbcb2e2","tid":1855920,"uid":33452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:27:11.000Z","msg":"長腿叔叔您好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182af5a268864b32392b41f88e01ac4ba67f3151","tid":1855920,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036d3f790f09d7acb0c7127ce919571c4cc14e48","tid":1855920,"uid":324041,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:29:12.000Z","msg":"而家口罩有價有市，D郵差會唔會&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b66979f80a16e92606054fc8f8c355111a3406","tid":1855920,"uid":51761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"多謝都郵差付出，辛苦哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dbcfe1f41553fecf694a6c1b3af712954ec46cd","tid":1855920,"uid":218684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8282c545f0f98b3d5e226dcf4d2e039d9128b6b","tid":1855920,"uid":47208,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"036d3f790f09d7acb0c7127ce919571c4cc14e48","tid":1855920,"uid":324041,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:29:12.000Z","msg":"而家口罩有價有市，D郵差會唔會&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"小人之心度君子之腹"},{"pid":"82125353d562ffb04114a7cb6a04f9a92c2c0a17","tid":1855920