來自內地的郵件，希望管理層短期內加強員工的防護裝備，部門已承諾若未能及時提供手套，員工可先行購買其後再申索有關金額。<br />\n<br />\n郵差叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7aFhkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7aFhkW.png&h=26c22fb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a81d7f3a718f6d85be6d828b04d37b8e7cc8fc6a","tid":1855920,"uid":13250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:42:21.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以自己拎？"},{"pid":"ac0be80a054967f16de9e825abb7c00620a1087d","tid":1855920,"uid":230416,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"早兩日個郵差上門派件嗰陣仲同我講新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地冒住風險都幫忙派送口罩畀大家，保障大家嘅健康，希望大家可以對佢地多少少關心</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72627813306c9c059d5b406ed7f70e073daa744f","tid":1855920,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f04fe564fcb8be25a0533574292dfda7dbcb2e2","tid":1855920,"uid":33452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:27:11.000Z","msg":"長腿叔叔您好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"香港小姐波波任我渣"},{"pid":"97e75d9e5e5d960145c84caafe0c356d25fe8ea2","tid":1855920,"uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"唔請炒散？"},{"pid":"c3342584f962dc7ae196b09996f6405b381566b1","tid":1855920,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a81d7f3a718f6d85be6d828b04d37b8e7cc8fc6a","tid":1855920,"uid":13250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:42:21.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以自己拎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:04:33.000Z","msg":"你入到機場禁區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66c3a9